between good and evil.

03:02.513 --> 03:05.232
Ohh!

03:05.256 --> 03:07.234
But they soon learn
that bad guys

03:07.258 --> 03:09.896
don't always look so bad.

03:09.920 --> 03:13.240
In fact, sometimes they even
seem downright friendly.

03:13.264 --> 03:16.848
That is, until you get to know
them a little bit better.

03:16.872 --> 03:18.345
Hey, fancy seeing you here.

03:18.369 --> 03:20.347
