03:39.920 --> 03:42.899
I'll do anything, but how
can I show you that I can...

03:42.923 --> 03:45.410
I can change if you don't
give me a second chance?

03:45.434 --> 03:46.733
Come on.

03:46.757 --> 03:48.575
You know I'm not a bad person.

03:48.599 --> 03:50.277
